===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|quaveren}}, frequentative form of {{m|enm|quaven}}, {{m|enm|cwavien||to tremble}}, equivalent to {{suffix|en|quave|er}}. Cognate with {{cog|nds|quabbeln||to quiver}}, {{cog|de|quabbeln}}, {{m|de|quappeln||to quiver}}. More at {{l|en|quave}}, {{l|en|quab}}, {{l|en|quiver}}.

